    <item>
      <title>Deadlines have a way of focusing the mind</title>
      <link>http://vielmetti.github.com/post/2014/2014-09-01-deadlines-have-a-way-of-focusing-the-mind/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Sep 2014 22:13:17 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://vielmetti.github.com/post/2014/2014-09-01-deadlines-have-a-way-of-focusing-the-mind/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;So I&#39;ve given myself an arbitrary deadline; write until the battery runs out, and then plug in and don&#39;t use the computer again for the day. At the very least I will type faster when the timer ticks down to 0:04. (The phone still has power though.)&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
